These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, spy, musical, time-travel, documentary, martial-arts, adventure
7 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, turtle, horse, dog, pony, rabbit
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the fish##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is between the owner of the turtle and the person watching musical movies##2
12. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | time-travel | musical  | documentary | comedy | spy | adventure |
| Pet           | turtle | fish   | rabbit | horse  | pony   | dog    | ferret    |

