.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, tea, fanta, juice, cola, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian, argentine, canadian, indonesian, thai, french
 1. the argentine is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the thai is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the argentine is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is between the indonesian and the brazilian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the argentine##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
11. the pakistani is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage      | tea | fanta | cola   | water | coffee | mirinda     | juice |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | pakistani  | indonesian | thai     | french  | argentine | canadian |

