7 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, goldfish, mouse, rabbit, frog, dog
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 8. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |     3      |      4      |      5      |       6       |     7      |
| Hobby   | photography  | fishing | singing | hiking | skydiving | traveling | cooking    |
| Pet     | rabbit | dog   | lizard       | mouse     | goldfish      | frog           | turtle |

