There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, italian, thai, american, egyptian, australian
 1. the canadian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the australian##1
 5. the canadian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the egyptian is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 9. the american is on the right of the australian##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the thai##3
11. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4   |     5     |       6       |    7    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | iced-tea     | almond-milk | tea | water      | fanta | mirinda  |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | italian   | pakistani | thai | australian       | american |

