.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, electrician, doctor, scientist, firefighter, dressmaker
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, ambient, punk, house, classical, soul, gospel
 1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 2. the fan of house is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 3. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the engineer is between the fan of gospel and the fan of classical##2
 7. the doctor is on the left of the firefighter##1
 8. the fan of soul is the dressmaker##1
 9. the engineer is on the left or right of the electrician##3
10. the fan of gospel is on the left of the scientist##1
11. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
12. the electrician is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
13. the fan of ambient is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |   2   |       3        |  4   |     5      |    6    |      7       |
| Job           | dressmaker | doctor | firefighter | engineer | electrician | scientist   | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | soul            | house | classical            | electronic  | gospel      | punk | ambient      |

