 4. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 6. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
