 9. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
11. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
13. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
14. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the fan of punk##1
15. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
