10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
11. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
13. the fan of ambient is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##2

