.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, photographer, nurse, engineer, fisherman, musician, bartender
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, family, disaster, comedy, satire, fantasy, musical
 1. the person watching musical movies is the engineer##1
 2. the journalist is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 3. the journalist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 4. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the engineer is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching family movies is between the person watching satire movies and the fisherman##2
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the musician##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
11. the person watching family movies is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Job           | engineer | journalist   | fisherman | nurse    | photographer   | bartender | musician     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | epic | comedy        | family | satire | fantasy   | disaster |

 